WEBVTT

00:01:41.879 --> 00:01:42.439
Hurry, let's go.

00:01:47.760 --> 00:01:49.359
Sister, Sister, come save me!

00:01:49.359 --> 00:01:50.159
Put this on.

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:50.760
Sister.

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:52.760
Hurry.

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:55.719
Let me out!

00:01:58.319 --> 00:01:59.640
Let me out!

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:05.200
There are guards stationed in the courtyard.

00:02:05.319 --> 00:02:06.519
Why lock another door?

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:10.000
Young Master.

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:11.840
With my status,

00:02:12.599 --> 00:02:13.879
being extra cautious

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:16.400
means less gossip.

00:02:23.199 --> 00:02:23.840
Please.

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:40.439
Get up.

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:43.599
Siniang, my legs are weak.

00:02:43.800 --> 00:02:44.719
I'll stay here and watch.

00:02:44.719 --> 00:02:45.680
Go call everyone here quickly.

00:02:45.919 --> 00:02:46.719
Go, hurry.

00:02:46.719 --> 00:02:47.360
Okay, okay.

00:02:48.199 --> 00:02:49.120
Then don't move from here.

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:50.080
I'll be right back.

00:03:27.039 --> 00:03:28.240
A room full of deeds.

00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:30.599
It is as if he

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:34.719
died in the business he built with his own hands.

00:03:36.800 --> 00:03:37.960
The primary cause of death was asphyxiation.

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:40.560
The time of death

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:42.840
should be at the start of the Hour of the Rabbit.

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:45.439
The Hour of the Rabbit.

00:03:47.439 --> 00:03:48.039
But why would he

00:03:48.639 --> 00:03:50.520
die in my room?

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:52.800
That is a question for you.

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:57.400
Were you not in your room last night?

00:03:59.680 --> 00:04:00.639
Recently, I...

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:02.800
I happened to be on my period.

00:04:03.520 --> 00:04:04.719
My lower abdomen was in pain.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:09.080
So I thought I'd take some painkillers.

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:12.360
But I found I was out of medicine.

00:04:13.759 --> 00:04:15.960
So I got up and went to the pharmacy.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:19.120
But when I left,

00:04:19.120 --> 00:04:20.680
I locked all the doors and windows.

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:22.759
I even double-checked them.

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:25.480
After I took the medicine,

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:28.240
I heard the patrol beating the watch.

00:04:30.120 --> 00:04:31.000
It was exactly the Hour of the Rabbit.

00:04:32.079 --> 00:04:34.600
I thought breakfast time was near,

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:37.000
so I went to the kitchen to make crispy pork for everyone.

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:38.199
Where is the key?

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:42.879
This black iron key is the only one.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:44.399
I always carry it with me.

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:46.160
If it were lost,

00:04:46.319 --> 00:04:47.399
a second one could not be made.

00:04:47.759 --> 00:04:48.720
If there are no witnesses,

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:51.439
this is just your one-sided story.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.160
When I went to the kitchen

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.680
and the pharmacy, I ran into servants.

00:04:58.759 --> 00:04:59.600
How about this, Siniang?

00:04:59.879 --> 00:05:01.160
Go find everyone who saw you last night

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:02.040
and bring them all here.

00:05:02.319 --> 00:05:02.720
Okay.

00:05:04.839 --> 00:05:05.560
How do I know

00:05:06.279 --> 00:05:07.360
if you are going to collude

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.120
or run away?

00:05:10.480 --> 00:05:11.879
I didn't think it through.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:12.720
Xiaobai.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:13.439
You go.

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:15.959
Call everyone who saw Siniang last night.

00:05:16.079 --> 00:05:16.839
Yes, Miss.

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:17.399
No need.

00:05:18.279 --> 00:05:19.000
Since you don't believe me,

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:20.160
just kill me with one slash.

00:05:22.480 --> 00:05:23.319
Let's talk this over calmly.

00:05:23.519 --> 00:05:24.480
Let's talk this over calmly.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:30.199
Ding Da died strangely.

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:31.519
My apprentice

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:32.839
was just anxious for a moment.

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:34.399
Siniang, don't take offense.

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:36.600
I apologize on behalf of my apprentice.

00:05:41.439 --> 00:05:42.199
Good lord.

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:44.240
A transaction of fifty thousand gold.

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:45.560
Are you alright?

00:05:46.360 --> 00:05:46.920
I'm fine.

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:14.399
Why is there water vapor here?

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:16.639
May I ask, Siniang,

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:19.279
did you burn anything in the brazier last night?

00:06:20.199 --> 00:06:21.319
The room was damp and cold,

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.879
so I burned a few pieces of charcoal.

00:06:25.279 --> 00:06:26.560
But there are no witnesses.

00:06:29.839 --> 00:06:30.920
That is strange.

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:32.240
If the fire was burned last night,

00:06:32.399 --> 00:06:34.759
why is there still water vapor on this table leg now?

00:06:42.439 --> 00:06:43.759
Don't you think that Liu Shiwu

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:44.959
is very strange?

00:06:45.839 --> 00:06:46.720
He rarely speaks,

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:48.000
yet he never misses a gathering.

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:51.439
Tell me,

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:53.560
could it be that the female ghost

00:06:54.519 --> 00:06:56.439
came to claim his soul?

00:06:57.959 --> 00:06:58.680
That makes sense.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:06:59.519
What sense does that make?

00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:03.040
This is clearly someone

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:06.360
committing premeditated murder.

00:07:07.839 --> 00:07:08.759
And the killer

00:07:09.959 --> 00:07:11.439
is right here in this villa.

00:07:20.839 --> 00:07:21.720
When Master Liu died,

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:25.279
everyone had an alibi.

00:07:26.519 --> 00:07:28.519
But why did the killer go to such lengths

00:07:28.519 --> 00:07:29.920
to burn down his courtyard?

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:33.639
Ding Da was clearly in his own room,

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.920
so how did he get to Siniang's room,

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:37.680
die inside,

00:07:38.839 --> 00:07:40.600
and have it staged as a locked-room murder?

00:07:42.199 --> 00:07:44.240
Master Liu and Zhang Shan's heads are missing,

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:45.879
so why is Ding Da's still here?

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:50.879
Do you have any theories?

00:07:53.079 --> 00:07:54.279
I did originally,

00:07:55.439 --> 00:07:56.839
but unfortunately, this fire

00:07:57.319 --> 00:07:59.279
and Ding Da's bizarre death have muddled them.

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:04.160
Master Kun,

00:08:04.879 --> 00:08:05.839
if you suspect me,

00:08:06.839 --> 00:08:07.839
then lock me up.

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:09.600
Regarding Ding Da's death,

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:10.879
I cannot escape responsibility either.

00:08:13.639 --> 00:08:14.439
As you said,

00:08:14.759 --> 00:08:17.040
we will settle the score after the case is solved.

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:21.240
Thank you, Lord Hua.

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:25.040
The reason cold cases are called such

00:08:25.439 --> 00:08:27.160
is often because most of the clues

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.120
are merely smoke and mirrors.

00:08:32.039 --> 00:08:34.519
People have habits when they think.

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:36.759
The killer exploited this habit,

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.200
leading the investigator

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:40.879
into a maze of his own design.

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:43.000
Therefore,

00:08:43.559 --> 00:08:44.720
don't overcomplicate things.

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:47.799
Often, the simplest answer is the correct one.

00:08:53.279 --> 00:08:53.919
Wait.

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:55.159
What is it?

00:09:01.080 --> 00:09:02.039
Something is wrong.

00:09:02.759 --> 00:09:03.600
Which part is wrong?

00:09:08.519 --> 00:09:09.600
Tell me.

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:17.480
Why is there blood here?

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:19.759
The two honored guests may not know,

00:09:19.960 --> 00:09:21.519
this is where we slaughter chickens and drain their blood.

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.039
The villa is an elegant place,

00:09:23.039 --> 00:09:23.840
so chicken cries are not permitted.

00:09:24.279 --> 00:09:25.360
Live chickens are brought in daily,

00:09:25.559 --> 00:09:26.919
and we slaughter them right here.

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:30.039
Master Kun,

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:34.200
look.

00:09:35.039 --> 00:09:37.679
Why would ants be interested in chicken blood?

00:09:45.879 --> 00:09:47.720
Is this cart used for delivering vegetables?

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:50.799
Outside carts are not allowed in the villa.

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:52.519
This one is used for deliveries within the villa.

00:10:03.039 --> 00:10:05.159
It matches the wheel tracks I found earlier.

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:08.080
Master Kun,

00:10:08.759 --> 00:10:11.279
do you remember that Master Liu was thin,

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:13.200
loved sweets, and drank a lot of tea?

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:14.799
That is Diabetes.

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:17.399
Patients with this condition have sugar in their blood.

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:20.240
If this blood belongs to Master Liu,

00:10:20.840 --> 00:10:21.720
then attracting ants

00:10:22.159 --> 00:10:23.120
would be normal.

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:24.600
So,

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:27.320
you are saying...

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:29.120
Didn't you just say

00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:32.679
that the killer exploits people's thinking habits

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:35.840
to lead the investigator into a maze?

00:10:37.039 --> 00:10:38.519
The place where the body is found

00:10:38.879 --> 00:10:40.960
is often assumed to be the crime scene.

00:10:41.559 --> 00:10:42.399
For example,

00:10:43.039 --> 00:10:44.519
Master Liu died in his room,

00:10:45.679 --> 00:10:46.720
but in reality...

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:04.600
Doctor Du called us over in a hurry,

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:05.799
did you find something?

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:07.519
Last night, right here,

00:11:07.799 --> 00:11:09.480
I found bloodstains that weren't burned away.

00:11:19.159 --> 00:11:19.960
Everyone, take a smell.

00:11:34.039 --> 00:11:35.159
Human blood smells metallic.

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:37.799
But this blood has a foul, gamey stench.

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:40.559
Also, blood that has flowed out

00:11:40.879 --> 00:11:42.960
turns black little by little over time.

00:11:43.639 --> 00:11:45.679
But the bloodstains by Master Liu's body

00:11:48.559 --> 00:11:49.720
are bright red.

00:11:51.279 --> 00:11:53.039
If Master Liu died two hours ago,

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:56.480
then this blood writing shouldn't be bright red.

00:11:57.320 --> 00:11:59.759
So Master Liu didn't die here.

00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:02.799
The blood was applied after the scene was staged.

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:04.679
Exactly.

00:12:05.039 --> 00:12:07.000
The killer went to great lengths to stage this

00:12:07.720 --> 00:12:09.200
just to lead everyone

00:12:09.639 --> 00:12:12.679
to think the body's location is the crime scene.

00:12:13.399 --> 00:12:17.320
To lead everyone down a false trail.

00:12:18.159 --> 00:12:19.000
Actually,

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:21.840
Master Liu didn't die here at all.

00:12:22.799 --> 00:12:23.559
Then where was it?

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:33.720
Come,

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:35.399
everyone smell this.

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:43.039
The smell is indeed different from before.

00:12:43.679 --> 00:12:45.399
Could this be human blood?

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:48.720
Luckily, this cart was parked here that night.

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:50.639
So that heavy rain

00:12:51.039 --> 00:12:52.759
didn't wash away all the bloodstains.

00:12:54.279 --> 00:12:55.440
Master Liu died here.

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:57.879
Since Master Liu died here,

00:12:58.720 --> 00:13:01.320
how did the body appear in his room?

00:13:02.080 --> 00:13:03.000
Even if Master Liu was thin,

00:13:04.399 --> 00:13:05.279
it's such a long way,

00:13:05.799 --> 00:13:08.120
moving the body would make noise.

00:13:08.840 --> 00:13:09.720
That isn't actually difficult.

00:13:10.919 --> 00:13:11.720
I guess

00:13:11.799 --> 00:13:13.639
the killer used the Thousand Mechanism Treasure as bait

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:15.480
to meet Master Liu here.

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:17.080
"I'm here, where are you?"

00:13:20.679 --> 00:13:21.039
"Well?"

00:13:21.159 --> 00:13:21.759
"Did you get the item?"

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.759
The killer couldn't silently

00:13:26.759 --> 00:13:28.039
move the body immediately.

00:13:28.360 --> 00:13:30.000
So they hid the body here first.

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:32.639
This path is behind the kitchen.

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:34.200
Except for servants and laborers,

00:13:34.559 --> 00:13:36.879
guests going to the main hall would never pass here.

00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:39.639
At night when everyone was asleep,

00:13:39.840 --> 00:13:40.600
the heavens helped,

00:13:40.720 --> 00:13:41.559
and it started raining again.

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:45.120
The rain masked the sound of moving the body,

00:13:45.639 --> 00:13:47.559
and the water washed away the evidence.

00:13:51.759 --> 00:13:53.600
But precisely because of this rain,

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:55.919
a trail of wheel tracks was left on the road.

00:13:57.519 --> 00:13:58.759
And the blood writing on the wall

00:13:59.200 --> 00:14:00.600
didn't use Master Liu's blood,

00:14:01.799 --> 00:14:03.639
but blood from killing a chicken here.

00:14:04.360 --> 00:14:05.080
Correct.

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:07.080
Writing with chicken blood,

00:14:07.519 --> 00:14:09.480
if discovered, all efforts would be wasted.

00:14:10.879 --> 00:14:13.919
So, the killer set fire to the room

00:14:14.799 --> 00:14:15.840
to destroy the evidence.

00:14:16.879 --> 00:14:19.279
So, who exactly is the killer?

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:20.440
Brother Aliang,

00:14:20.799 --> 00:14:21.480
don't rush.

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:23.000
The killer

00:14:25.720 --> 00:14:26.879
will appear very soon.